Russia’s RTS Stock-Index Futures Advance at Start of Trading

-- B y   H a l i a   P a v l i v a
-- 
2011-03-15T16:51:27Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-15/russia-s-rts-stock-index-futures-advance-at-start-of-trading.html
  Russia ’s RTS stock-index futures
expiring in June gained at the start of trading, advancing 0.4
percent to 186,425 at 12:28 p.m. in  New York .  Contracts on OAO Sberbank, Russia’s largest lender, and OAO
Gazprom, the natural-gas export monopoly, gained 0.4 percent.
Contracts on OAO Lukoil, the country’s second-biggest oil
producer, rose 0.6 percent. The Market Vectors Russia ETF, a
U.S.-traded fund that holds Russian shares, fell 2.6 percent.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Halia Pavliva in New York at 
